@XavierGeerinck I tried to reproduce this issue using demo_actor app, but I could not.

According to the log that you attached, I do not think it is related to aiohttp bug because the response seems to overlap the previously received data rather than truncate the data. ActorProxy is asynchronous calls, but seems like you make this async call to sync call in multiple threads. It might be the root cause of this problem. 

Can you please share your code?

> Good we found it, but this does not need a 0.9.1 release and is not under the definition of P0.

Ok make sense. @XavierGeerinck i will provide the way to use the fix.

@yaron2 btw, are we validating response for each call in invocation perf test ? Then this would have to be discoverable..
